chunks.en: Does your company have a New Year's red envelope?
chunks.zh: 大家公司有开年红包吗？

chunks.en:
I'll start: 
Located in Hangzhou, none.
chunks.zh:
我先来：
坐标杭州，无。

chunks.en: It's always 20 every year. These three 20 bills are quietly lying on my bedside table. I have no chance and can't remember to spend them. I plan to take them to my mother when I go home for the New Year next year.
chunks.zh: 每年都是 20 ，这三张 20 纸币都静静地躺在我床头柜里，没机会也想不起来花出去我计划明年过年回家的时候，带给我妈

chunks.en: A note was stuffed in the red envelope, which read: 88 points. It can only be spent in its own mall, worth about 8 yuan. I would think it's too small to be toilet paper.
chunks.zh: 红包里塞了个纸条，写着：88 积分。只能在自己商城消费，大概值 8 块钱，当厕纸我都嫌太小。

chunks.en: 100 and also deduct taxes from the salary
